Package jSimPack

A discrete event simulator

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BreakpointListener
    Implement this class to register and respond to breakpoints in the future event list.
    EventHandler
    Responds to events released by a FutureEventList.
    FutureEventListener
    Receives notification when events are released from a FutureEventList.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BreakpointPrinter
    Utility class that prints a message when a breakpoint occurs.
    FutureEvent
    Data object that encodes event information.
    FutureEventList
    Dispatches abstract events that occur at discrete points in time.
    PrintDataEvent
    A utility class that prints the callback object to stdout when the event occurs.
    PrintEvent
    Utility class that prints a string when the scheduled event occurs.
    RandomSource
    Wrapper class for Random that lets us manage the random seed.
    ScheduleOtherEvent  
    SimTime
    This class offers a units-aware represenation of simulation time.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SimTime.SimTimeUnit
